{"tid":498891,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"盧卡古值9000萬證明左當今足球界好識吹奏","createTime":"2017-12-14T08:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-14T10:05:42.000Z","uid":108894,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f4de9b6df968ee2f7bd29f56833645e29ad981e4","tid":498891,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:24:45.000Z","msg":"盧卡古呢位仁兄，係就係入左十幾球，但係其他前鋒嘅工作唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無制空做唔到前場支點，無控球唔可以帶領反擊，無傳球唔止終結進攻仲做埋對面反擊發動者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唯一作用就係禁區入面等頂等射，仲要又唔係好勁果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個現今世代嘅前鋒佢根本唔入流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完完全全因為傳媒同球迷吹奏先值9000萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (的的確確佢係愛記又踢得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果盧卡古有9000萬，朗拿度，雲佬，亨利，舒利亞呢D起碼值5億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反伊巴就真係值9000萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，35，36歲都交足貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哈利簡尼，加比爾捷西斯，拿卡錫迪，莫拉達都比盧卡古更值9000萬"},{"pid":"c920ff2b833c5152eebf6e3e04ad4e0256f57431","tid":498891,"uid":147527,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:27:27.000Z","msg":"樓主打左針未"},{"pid":"1b9c6df2d7aa27a844698025408fe37d544bc114","tid":498891,"uid":108894,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T08:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主打左針未</blockquote><br />\n獌狗出黎咬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132ec8dc737b9ff3000011f47d7267556be88d8