dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 伊巴有用過佢百萬倍"},{"pid":"dac626ef5662c06f031763977565fc94eefb476c","tid":498891,"uid":74123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"佢係愛記駁撚哂老命咪又係想比大球會睇中<br />\n到過左曼聯 打左排一無波入 就接受唔到批評<br />\n頂唔順啲壓力 有幾場我睇佢個樣直程成隻病貓咁<br />\n踢到落哂形  <br />\n琴晚入完波都唔慶祝 我諗佢自己都知衰<br />\n再比啲時間應該會有改變"},{"pid":"c98d2c9b7e130083303171a3cdcaffe82c6e414b","tid":498891,"uid":159523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>值唔值由樓主話事</blockquote><br />\n有冇睇舒利亞係曼市打吡點屌盧卡古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qBFA5WXAVQ4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqBFA5WXAVQ4&d=y%2Fqd8MyStx9%2BQdFqO2ApWozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8fa36535\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qBFA5WXAVQ4</a></blockquote><br />\n我曼唔使比狃評價"},{"pid":"4df81624ad3b3329e721d981115d57333512fe58","tid":498891,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"牙朗呢位仁兄，係就係入左幾十球，但係其他前鋒嘅工作唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無制空做唔到前場支點，無控球唔可以帶領反擊，無傳球唔止終結進攻仲做埋對面反擊發動者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唯一作用就係禁區入面等頂等射，仲要又唔係好勁果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個現今世代嘅前鋒佢根本唔入流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完完全全因為傳媒同球迷吹奏先值8000萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (的的確確佢係獌狗又踢得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果牙朗有8000萬，朗拿度，雲佬，亨利，舒利亞呢D起碼值5億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反伊巴就真係值8000萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，35，36歲都交足貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哈利簡尼，加比爾捷西斯，拿卡錫迪，莫拉達都比牙朗更值8000萬"},{"pid":"40b7f40495d86af94297a619a30eb08c7137704d","tid":498891,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:03:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牙朗呢位仁兄，係就係入左幾十球，但係其他前鋒嘅工作唔合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無制空做唔到前場支點，無控球唔可以帶領反擊，無傳球唔止終結進攻仲做埋對面反擊發動者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢唯一作用就係禁區入面等頂等射，仲要又唔係好勁果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為一個現今世代嘅前鋒佢根本唔入流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完完全全因為傳媒同球迷吹奏先值8000萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (的的確確佢係獌狗又踢得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n如果牙朗有8000萬，朗拿度，雲佬，亨利，舒利亞呢D起碼值5億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反伊巴就真係值8000萬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，35，36歲都交足貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n哈利簡尼，加比爾捷西斯，拿卡錫迪，莫拉達都比牙朗更值8000萬</blockquote><br />\nC.朗都講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d4e419c56d4da5a9f0242fa4f7fe1f50a578f7","tid":498891,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T10:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係愛記駁撚哂老命咪又係想比大球會睇中<br />\n到過左曼聯 打左排一無波入 就接受唔到批評<br />\n頂唔順啲壓力 有幾場我睇佢個樣直程成隻病貓咁<br />\n踢到落哂形  <br />\n琴晚入完波都唔慶祝 我諗佢自己都知衰<br />\n再比啲時間應該會有改變</blockquote><br />\n其實盧卡古係愛記都有季入球唔多<br />\n而且佢之前都已經比人話做唔到制空點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，應該係positioning本身差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}